Description of incident: Dungarees has notified individuals of a data breach when they discovered their online store was hacked. The  hacking may have been compromised both debit and credit card numbers.  The hacking may have compromised customer names, billing information,  mailing information email addresses, credit and debit card information,  the expiration dated, the CVV on the back of the card. More information: http://oag.ca.gov/ecrime/databreach/reports/sb24-59371
